    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029820/extras/5d87b2da8d5df40e31814792835f6abc.poster.avif?t=1727530041\" width=620 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029820/extras/5d87b2da8d5df40e31814792835f6abc.webm?t=1727530041\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029820/extras/5d87b2da8d5df40e31814792835f6abc.mp4?t=1727530041\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏介绍</h2>   《Ai Vpet/守护与智友》是一款创新的AI虚拟桌宠软件，它突破了传统桌面宠物的局限，通过深度学习和自然语言处理等AI技术，为用户提供了一个知识渊博、能言善辩的AI伴侣。用户可以根据自己的喜好，选择和定制各种角色模型，包括服装、宠物、性格和声音等，打造一个完全个性化的专属虚拟伙伴。<br>   在用户需要专注工作时它会安静的陪伴，在用户需要休息时它会主动发起互动，增加工作和生活的趣味性。《Ai Vpet/守护与智友》不仅仅是一个桌面装饰工具，更是一个能够提供情感寄托、知识学习和生活娱乐的全方位AI朋友。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>产品特色</strong></h2>一、高自由度的模型兼容可以让您定制角色的每一个细节，海量资源免费任你挑选，从性格到声音，从IP联名到自创角色，您可以随心搭配定制，打造专宠你一人的智友。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029820/extras/238563ffdde87fadb1bf1521912ccb33.poster.avif?t=1727530041\" width=540 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029820/extras/238563ffdde87fadb1bf1521912ccb33.webm?t=1727530041\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029820/extras/238563ffdde87fadb1bf1521912ccb33.mp4?t=1727530041\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br>二、《Ai Vpet/守护与智友》通过先进的AI技术，为用户提供AI情感陪伴功能，它就像一个真实的朋友，能够和你随时开启聊天互动，让你的生活充满惊喜和乐趣。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029820/extras/f712880c527831dcbe44c295bd1e7368.poster.avif?t=1727530041\" width=540 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029820/extras/f712880c527831dcbe44c295bd1e7368.webm?t=1727530041\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029820/extras/f712880c527831dcbe44c295bd1e7368.mp4?t=1727530041\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br>三、从人物形象到性格、服装到声音，各种人物，宠物，摆件随意diy组合。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029820/extras/bf5e09423eb89c699136acdf4c760a53.poster.avif?t=1727530041\" width=540 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029820/extras/bf5e09423eb89c699136acdf4c760a53.webm?t=1727530041\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029820/extras/bf5e09423eb89c699136acdf4c760a53.mp4?t=1727530041\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>四、我们采用业界领先的Live2D技术，每一个角色都如艺术品般栩栩如生，动作流畅至极，极致的视觉盛宴，超多交互动画让人心动。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029820/extras/da375f01c2e962a70e454f8af4a5666c.poster.avif?t=1727530041\" width=540 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029820/extras/da375f01c2e962a70e454f8af4a5666c.webm?t=1727530041\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029820/extras/da375f01c2e962a70e454f8af4a5666c.mp4?t=1727530041\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>五、模型上传工具，满足不同用户的需求。无论是小白，还是专家，都能轻松驾驭，快速完成模型的设置和上传。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029820/extras/a8e65f5d40ed8768d271febb378fd2aa.poster.avif?t=1727530041\" width=540 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029820/extras/a8e65f5d40ed8768d271febb378fd2aa.webm?t=1727530041\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029820/extras/a8e65f5d40ed8768d271febb378fd2aa.mp4?t=1727530041\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>制作团队的心里话</strong></h2><br>  我们深知，一款优秀的桌面助手不仅仅是一个工具，更是您数字生活中不可或缺的伙伴。《Ai Vpet/守护与智友》的诞生，是我们对这一理念的坚持和追求。我们承诺，将不断更新和改进，以满足您的需求和期望。每一条反馈，每一次建议，都是我们前进的动力，我们珍视您的声音，因为我们知道没有您的支持和参与，《Ai Vpet/守护与智友》不会如此生动和完善。<br>  在这个快节奏的时代，我们希望《Ai Vpet/守护与智友》能为您带来一丝宁静和便捷。我们致力于通过个性化定制，让您的AI虚拟宠物与众不同，成为您个性的延伸。我们相信，通过AI互动聊天，它不仅能帮助您管理日常任务，更能成为您生活中的一位有趣和智能的对话伙伴。<br>  我们感谢您选择《Ai Vpet/守护与智友》作为您的AI虚拟宠物。我们期待着与您一起，不断探索和创造，让《Ai Vpet/守护与智友》成为您桌面上最闪耀的那颗星。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>请关注我们</strong></h2>掌握官方最新动态，请关注",
